### E-commerce Website Testing 


## Project Included

### E-commerce Website Testing

This project focuses on manual testing of an **E-commerce web application** to verify the functionality, usability, and correctness of key user workflows. Testing was performed on major modules such as **login, product page, cart, checkout, shipping details, and order confirmation**.


## Project Objective

The objective of this project is to test the core functionalities of the application, identify defects in different modules, and document the findings using structured testing artifacts such as **test cases** and **bug reports**.


## Application Type

**Web-based E-commerce Application**

## Modules Tested

The following modules were covered during testing:

* Login
* Product Page
* Cart
* Checkout
* Shipping Details
* Order Confirmation

## Testing Scope

The testing scope included validation of the following functionalities:

* User login validation
* Product name and product description verification
* Reset App State functionality
* Product quantity and size selection validation
* Cart and checkout behavior
* Order placement validation
* Shipping information validation
* Order confirmation details verification


## Testing Types Performed

* Functional Testing
* Negative Testing
* Validation Testing
* UI Testing
* Defect Reporting

## Deliverables Included

This repository contains the following project documents:

* **01_Project_Overview.docx** – Project overview, scope, modules covered, testing types, and tools used
* **02_Test_Cases.xlsx** – Test cases designed for different modules and workflows
* **03_Bug_Report.xlsx** – Bug log containing identified defects with bug details, severity, and status
* **04_Bug_Report.docx** – Formal bug report document summarizing the defects identified during testing

## Key Defects Identified

Some of the defects identified during testing include:

* SQL Injection vulnerability in login functionality
* Product name mismatch on product page
* Product description mismatch
* Reset App State not working as expected
* Quantity selection option not available before adding product to cart
* Size selection option not available before adding product to cart
* User able to place an order with no products in cart
* Invalid postal codes accepted by the application
* Address and phone number missing in shipping details
* Order ID not displayed after order confirmation


## Tools Used

* Manual Testing
* Microsoft Excel
* Microsoft Word
* Google Chrome

